Ἐν τῷ καλῷ<lb/>
τόπῳ μνησθῇ<lb/>
Ἱέρι<add>ο</add>ς μετὰ τῆς<lb/>
σθμβίου καὶ τέκ<lb/>
νων κα<add>ὶ</add> Ἰουλι<lb/>
νὸς καὶ Εὐτο<lb/>
κία σύμβιος. 

		  </p>
</div>
<div ana="#b1" corresp="#hamm0055.diplomatic #hamm0055.transcription" type="translation" xml:id="hamm0055.translation">
<p>
<rs type="formula">In this beautiful place </rs> may <persName ref="persons.xml#hamm0055p01" xml:lang="la ">Hierius </persName> be remembered, with (his) <rs type="family">wife </rs> and <rs type="family">children</rs>, and <persName ref="persons.xml#hamm0055p02" xml:lang="grc ">Julian </persName> and (his) <rs type="family">wife </rs>
